The Southern Bastion (Vigil of the Border): The castle’s southern wall faces the distant Barren Lands. It is a formidable, crenellated bastion of iron‑grey stone, where the Moniyan knights keep eternal watch. The Beacon of the Southern Star, a massive, silver‑white flame, burns perpetually at its summit. Tiny sentries stand guard.

Silvanna — The Imperial Knight Princess (Character Cartouche): Integrated seamlessly into the lower‑right corner, in the foreground near the edge of the Reflecting Pool, is a dedicated, framed Character Landmark Section. It depicts Princess Silvanna, standing in a regal yet battle‑ready pose. She is tall and noble, with long, flowing silver‑white hair beneath a delicate, winged tiara. She wears ornate, silver‑and‑white imperial plate armour with a short, flowing blue‑and‑white battle skirt. In her right hand, she holds her massive, radiant holy lance, its tip glowing with a warm, golden‑white light. Her expression is serene but deeply sorrowful, her gaze fixed on the distant Barren Lands. Below her portrait, a tiny vermilion cartouche reads her name and title: Silvanna — The Lance of Light and Princess of Aberleen.

